{"tid":1112078,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"近日係youtube睇到個問題，幾有意思","createTime":"2019-04-17T08:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T10:36:53.000Z","uid":206463,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f30692112052ca2756f04598f803671cbc851a17","tid":1112078,"uid":206463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"本身係一個鐘意諗野嘅人，近排喺youtube見到有條片講個問題幾有意思<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n從前有條村入面有6個藍色眼嘅人，2個紅色眼嘅人<br />\n佢哋有個規則就係<br />\n<br />\n1）見到人哋隻眼嘅顏色唔可以同人講<br />\n2）知道自己隻眼嘅顏色嘅人第二日要自殺<br />\n<br />\n有一日有個旅行家黎到呢個村莊<br />\n就講呢條村有紅色眼嘅人<br />\n之後兩個紅眼嘅人就死咗<br />\n<br />\n假如呢條村只有6個藍眼 1 個紅眼<br />\n咁自然紅眼嗰個就知道自己隻眼嘅顏色然後去自殺啦<br />\n<br />\n但係點解有2個紅眼，最後2個都會去自殺？<br />\n<br />\n旅行家講嘅野佢地其實一早就知，點解會令佢哋自殺？<br />\n<br />\n原來當其中一個紅眼無去自殺，佢就知紅眼係有1個以上，而其他人除咗1個紅眼其他都唔係，所以自己就係紅眼，之後佢地就會去一齊自殺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而因為其中村入面既人唔知其他人知唔知村有紅眼<br />\n所以當一個人講到大家都知，所以先會有2個紅眼去自殺<br />\n片中稱為共有知識同公共知識<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n歡迎大家討論 同分享多啲呢類型嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次出文 多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3356ade33ff965c9cab8088085911f442b8b8aeb","tid":1112078,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YPH4kC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YPH4kC.png&h=5c8a1063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbN6My1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbN6My1.png&h=9ea60d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xeHuKkJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxeHuKkJ.png&h=5be27a4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"300f55cf2d4d470a6dd55dc490b591459ebbe44a","tid":1112078,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宇智波一族咩 屌"}]}